features.text: YETI MFER MINI GAME BATTLE HISTORY

#
  SNOW BATTLE

#
 RULES
SET YOUR GRAPHICS TO LOW, IF MODELS DO NOT LOAD TRY REFRESHING THE BROWSER.

  | RULES   |
  | ----------- |:---------:|
  | 1.          | READ ALL THE INFORMATION BEFORE PLAYING, THIS IS THE START OF FUTURE GREAT EXPERIENCES.    |
  | 2.          | AT THE FINISH TAKE A WONP WHERE YOUR SCORE IS SEEN THIS IS NECESSARY TO KEEP A PUBLIC RECORD OF THE SCORES.  |
  | 3.          | ANNIHILATE  5   ENEMIE DORNES  WITH YOUR LOAD OF AMMUNITION (SNOWBALLS)     |
  | 4.          | MFER COLLECTS THE 10 ETH SYMBOL COINS|
| 5.          |SIGN THE GUEST BOOK TO CLAIM ETHMFE COINS, THESE COINS WILL BE BURNED TO CLAIM PRIZES 3K SUPPLY(THE BOOK WILL BE RESTARTED EVERY WEEK SO PLAYERS CAN CLAIM MORE COINS)|
| 6.          | KEEP IT REAL AND ENJOY|
#
INSTRUCTIONS
To start CLICK ON THE BLUE BUTTON you will have 80 seconds to eliminate the enemy drones and womp your score, Hey YetiMfer everyone wants your head so survive and hit all the DRONES with snowballs, these machines want your Head, collect the coins needed to survive and travel to multiple dimensions, don't forget to sign the guestbook to claim the weekly supply of coins, this will take you to the next level.

#
CREATED BY:
DIRECTION AND DESIGN BY:

fuzzyface.eth / @DCOT15 on Twitter

SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT BY:

misfitpixels.eth / @MisfitPIXELS on Twitter

Support:

CREYVOXELS AND CREYZIES, FINEARTMFERS



 
#
HISTORY

YOU HAVE AN UNKNOWN ORIGIN IN ANOTHER LIFE YOU ARE SARTOSHI'S FRIEND. KEEP YOUR IDENTITY UNDER PROFILE.
SO YOU ARE A RARE GUY TO FIND, SOME MACHINES ARE FILM TO REVEAL YOUR LOCATION AND FILTER IMAGES OF MFERYETI, YOU MUST DESTROY THE DRONES THAT SURVEILLANCE THE PLACE, YOU ARE A MFER WILL SEARCH FOR COINS PICK UP AND BURN TO TRAVEL NEW EXPERIENCES AND OBTAIN OBJECTS COLLECTION THAT CAN GRANT POWERS AND ABILITIES WITHIN THE GAME.
